<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>When the <db:link xlink:href="qml-qt3d-render-pointsize.xml#sizeMode-prop">sizeMode</db:link> property is set to SizeMode::Fixed, the value is set using glPointSize(), if available. When using SizeMode::Programmable, gl_PointSize must be set within shader programs, the value provided to this <db:link xlink:href="qml-qt3d-render-renderstate.xml">RenderState</db:link> is ignored in that case.</db:para>
</db:section>
<db:section xml:id="property-documentation">
<db:title>Property Documentation</db:title>
<db:section xml:id="sizeMode-prop">
<db:title>sizeMode : enumeration</db:title>
<db:para>Specifies the sizeMode to be used.</db:para>
</db:section>
<db:section xml:id="value-prop">
<db:title>value : real</db:title>
<db:para>Specifies the point size value to be used.</db:para>
</db:section>
